<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2093:2120'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-10b' );" name="082-10b" class="pb">[082-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2120:2123'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2123:2148'>　案閒𫝊云斬衰貌若苴齊衰貌若枲喪服𫝊曰苴絰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2148:2171'>　大搹左本在下爾雅以蕡為枲實孫炎以蕡為麻子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2171:2194'>　苴絰者以色言之謂之苴以實言之謂之蕡鄭氏康</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2194:2217'>　成曰麻在首在腰皆曰絰絰之言實也明孝子有忠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2217:2240'>　實之心苴之形惡色貌象苴服因心而發也盈手曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2240:2263'>　搹搹扼也圍九寸　腰絰大七寸五分寸之一而樛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2263:2286'>　之謂兩股相交兩頭結各存麻本散垂三尺也　絞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2286:2309'>　帶者繩帶也謂絞苴麻為繩以作帶故云絞帶王肅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2309:2336'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-11a' );" name="082-11a" class="pb">[082-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2336:2350'>　謂帶如腰絰亦用苴麻為之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2350:2377'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-12a' );" name="082-12a" class="pb">[082-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
</p>
