<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4327:4330'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4330:4333'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4333:4336'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4336:4339'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4339:4342'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4342:4345'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4345:4372'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-25b' );" name="082-25b" class="pb">[082-25b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4372:4395'>　案喪大記小斂君錦衾大夫縞衾士緇衾皆一至大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4395:4418'>　斂又制二衾君大夫士一也凡衾皆五幅布於絞上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4418:4441'>　衾者即今之被也紟者鄭注襌被也五幅白布為之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4441:4464'>　別無緣飾喪大記云紟五幅無紞注云紞被識生時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4464:4487'>　襌被有識死則去之異於生也　喪大記曰小斂以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4487:4510'>　往用夷衾夷衾質殺之裁猶冒也冒以韜屍小斂又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4510:4533'>　覆以夷衾其所用繒色及長短制度與質殺同但不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4533:4556'>　復為囊及旁綴耳小斂前有冒故不用夷衾自小斂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4556:4583'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-26a' );" name="082-26a" class="pb">[082-26a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4583:4599'>　後衣多不可用冒故用夷衾覆之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4599:4626'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-27a' );" name="082-27a" class="pb">[082-27a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4626:4629'>　</span><br/>
