<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='5763:5786'>　案禮記喪大記曰熬君四種八筐大夫三種六筐士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='5786:5809'>　二種四筐加魚腊焉注熬者以火熬穀使香以筐盛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='5809:5832'>　之設棺旁以惑蚍蜉使不至棺也鄭注士喪禮曰熬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='5832:5855'>　黍稷各二筐又曰設熬旁各一筐大夫三種加以粱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='5855:5878'>　君四種加以稻四筐則手足各一餘設於左右加魚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='5878:5901'>　腊者案特牲士腊用兔少牢大夫腊用麋天子諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='5901:5924'>　無文當用六獸之屬今案用熬筐者或亦以穀氣者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='5924:5947'>　人精氣所依置之棺旁亦實口用米實鬲用飯之意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='5947:5974'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-32a' );" name="082-32a" class="pb">[082-32a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='5974:5997'>　必謂以惑蚍蜉竊恐熬穀易竭而蚍蜉無窮也迂矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='5997:6024'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-33a' );" name="082-33a" class="pb">[082-33a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
