<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='6424:6447'>　案天子六綍前後二碑上下各重鹿盧共穿四綍左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='6447:6466'>　右二碑二鹿盧分穿二綍餘可以此推之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='6466:6493'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-36a' );" name="082-36a" class="pb">[082-36a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
