<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='6544:6567'>　案士喪禮為銘各以其物檀弓銘明旌也以死者為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='6567:6590'>　不可別已故以其旗識之注云明旌神明之旌也周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='6590:6613'>　禮司常大喪共銘旌注云王則大常　又案司常職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='6613:6643'>　王建大常諸侯建旗孤卿建<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0950' title='KR0950' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0950.png'/>大夫士建物銘旌亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='6643:6666'>　然但尺數異耳天子九尺諸侯七尺大夫五尺士三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='6666:6689'>　尺若不命之士則以緇布半幅長一尺也赬其末長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='6689:6712'>　終幅長二尺也緇赬共長三尺廣三寸書銘於末曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='6712:6735'>　某氏某之柩竹杠長三尺置于宇西階上注云杠銘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='6735:6762'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0068', 'WYG', '082-37a' );" name="082-37a" class="pb">[082-37a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
